{
  "stem": "13096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were depositing in the-- in the gate, big basket of fruits, big basket of-- even we didn't know who it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were just depositing them into-- to-- to be given to the prisoner there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were very good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Italians, they were very, very good to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, after three days, then they-- they-- they-- they make, you know, like the alarm, when the, you know, people, you know, they were having bombardment before.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after, they were-- they were given the siren, you know, to let know, you know, that there was something coming.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They make it-- the siren blew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everybody, the-- the Italian population and the Greek, whatever, they thought some bombs were coming, you know-- some airplanes were coming.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, they were Jewish to be evacuated to the port.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't want everybody-- when they, you know, usually, they heard that noise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to go to their shelter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that particular day, it wasn't any bombs-- any, you know, allies, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans, they didn't want the-- the-- the population to see what was happen to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, as I was saying before, during, you know, the previous years, they was happened that three, four of our Jewish girl married, you know, out of faith.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when they heard, and they were, you know, protected for the time being by their husband, and their children, and this and that-- when they heard what was happening to the Jewish population, they left their husband, and they come and-- and joined the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they thought, you know, they made a mistake marrying, you know, out of faith.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
